<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Search for Spring endpoints</b></p><p>In a Spring application, you can find an endpoint using the <span class="control">Search Everywhere</span> dialog. Press <span class="shortcut">Shift</span> twice and type <span class="code_emphasis">/url</span> to filter by endpoint URLs. For your convenience, there is also the <span class="control">Go To URL Mapping</span> action mapped to <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:GotoUrlAction;</span>.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/spring_goto_symbol.png" alt="Navigating the Spring application by URL" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>